ltTemplate(): Template {\n  return {\n    name: 'default',\n    render: (content: string, data: Record<string, unknown>) => {\n      return `<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>${data.title || ''} | ${data.siteTitle || ''}</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <article>\n    <h1>${data.title || ''}</h1>\n    ${data.date ? `<time>${data.date}</time>` : ''}\n    <div class=\"content\">${content}</div>\n  </article>\n</body>\n</html>`;\n    }\n  };\n}\n\nexport function createListTemplate(): Template {\n  return {\n    name: 'list',\n    render: (content: string, data: Record<string, unknown>) => {\n      return `<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>${data.title || ''} | ${data.siteTitle || ''}</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>${data.title || ''}</h1>\n  <div class=\"list\">${content}</div>\n</body>\n</html>`;\n    }\n  };\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Test Files\n\n### tests/core.test.ts (15 tests - MUST PASS)\nComplete file with comprehensive tests for:\n- Plugin registration\n- Template registration\n- HTML rendering with templates\n- Plugin hooks (beforeBuild, transformContent, afterBuild)\n- Plugin dependency resolution with topological sort\n- Circular dependency detection\n- Missing dependency detection\n- Multiple plugin transformations in order\n- Shared data store in build context\n- File metadata retention\n- Empty file list handling\n\n### tests/plugins/markdown-ext.test.ts (8 tests)\nTests for `createMarkdownExtPlugin()`:\n- Basic markdown to HTML conversion\n- Footnotes with [^1] syntax\n- Footnote section rendering\n- Admonition containers (:::note, :::warning, :::tip)\n- HTML preservation\n- Empty content handling\n\n### tests/plugins/asset-pipeline.test.ts (9 tests)\nTests for `createAssetPipelinePlugin()`:\n- Rewrite relative image URLs to /assets/\n- Rewrite relative link URLs to /assets/\n- Leave absolute URLs unchanged\n- Generate asset manifest in ctx.data\n- Handle multiple assets\n- Prevent double-p